[Gravitational Propulsion]
Any machine or device capable of traveling through the direct interaction of it's parts with gravity and space. Picture the Einstein model of a gravitational field warping space due to mass influence. A Direct Gravitational Propulsion device interacts with warped space, or warps space in order to propel.

